data.description: Discover the charm of this 4-bedroom, 3-bath home situated in Osgood area. Set on a 1/3-acre lot, this gem features a fully landscaped and fenced yard, a spacious 3-car garage, and a basement wet bar perfect for entertaining. Inside, the open-concept living space boasts ample windows, creating an inviting atmosphere. The kitchen offers a wrap-around feel, and the main level hosts the primary bedroom with ensuite, two additional bedrooms, and a bathroom. The fully finished basement provides a wet bar and ample space for fun and games. Your dream home is ready for you – schedule a visit today! Explore the possibilities with a assumable VA loan at 2.25%. Contact the listing agent for more details. This home comes with a pre-listing inspection by the Idaho Elite Inspection Team for added peace of mind.
